{"tid":2272304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「譚德塞等我」 拜登豪言一當選首要事情是重返世衞！","createTime":"2020-11-05T03:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T07:43:18.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"00ad780de23ee8a70c6caee76ab9155835f22d8b","tid":2272304,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"美國國務院及聯合國表示，美國已向聯合國秘書長古特雷斯（Ant&oacute;nio Guterres）提出正式離開世衛的通知，會在2021年7月6日生效。國務院又指，會繼續尋求改革世衛。<br />\n<br />\n拜登隨即在社交平台Twitter撰文指：<br />\n<br />\n「當美國致力加強全球健康，美國人就會更安全。在擔任總統的第一天，我會重新加入世衛，恢復我們在世界舞台上的領導地位。」<br />\n（Americans are safer when America is engaged in strengthening global health. On my first day as President, I will rejoin the @WHO and restore our leadership on the world stage.）"},{"pid":"ee2ac7d8f1a1bba495ede54088911ea5cd808f78","tid":2272304,"uid":79562,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:52:56.000Z","msg":"支持國際組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.fountmedia.io/upload_image/articleListCover/articleListCover_729a29d9b82de4d15a43e11332d450cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fountmedia.io%2Fupload_image%2FarticleListCover%2FarticleListCover_729a29d9b82de4d15a43e11332d450cb.jpg&h=95aa0b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2019年世界糧食計劃署的資金，有43%來自美國，0.06%來自中國。</strong><br />\n <br />\n世界糧食計劃署（World FoodProgramme）榮獲2020年諾貝爾和平獎的殊榮。國際問題專家汪浩今（10）日指出，2019年世界糧食計劃署的資金43%來自美國，0.06%來自中國，直批習近平「構建人類命運共同體」，出張嘴，不出錢。"},{"pid":"6cabb73ee5ab09dcb5b36f911b6168bb7d32d759","tid":2272304,"uid":76804,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:54:04.000Z","msg":"其實侵侵退出曬全部國際組織<br />\n比中共壟斷曬<br />\n而美國自己又唔另起爐灶 都唔係好事"},{"pid":"5a1084bc5737230340a8c0091baa8f75aba51f25","tid":2272304,"uid":155095,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:54:31.000Z","msg":"譚德塞：又有人送錢俾我，賺完人仔又賺美金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" 